longBusinessSummary: G2 Technologies Corp. does not have significant operations. It focuses on developing opportunities in clean tech and emerging technologies. The company was formerly known as Green 2 Blue Energy Corp. and changed its name to G2 Technologies Corp. in October 2020. G2 Technologies Corp. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
